"price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2067767726974570815", "url": "https://x.com/NuggetCapital/status/2067767726974570815", "text": "Agree with Citi which makes me nervous. #oott", "time": "00:33", "author": "NuggetCapital", "author_name": "Nugget Capital Partners (NCP)", "followers": 7677, "views": 6100, "likes": 21, "replies": 6, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2067839010907861112", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067839010907861112", "text": "Pakistan LNG has cancelled its spot tender for a prompt LNG cargo that was due to close today, as a laden QatarEnergy tanker heads toward Port Qasim following its transit of the Strait of Hormuz. #LNG @Kpler #OOTT", "time": "05:16", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 14774, "likes": 79, "replies": 2, "retweets": 14, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Natural gas", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067859190752678035", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067859190752678035", "text": "Aggregated open interest in Brent and WTI in million contracts #oott https://t.co/qghneat9sO", "time": "06:37", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 11577, "likes": 16, "replies": 0, "retweets": 4, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2067859359715958913", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067859359715958913", "text": "Brent futures curve in USD/bbl (today, one week ago and one month ago) #OOTT https://t.co/u1ScNQAFrL", "time": "06:37", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 8347, "likes": 14, "replies": 0, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2067884574554628133", "url": "https://x.com/TankerTrackers/status/2067884574554628133", "text": "Iran has exported nearly 18 million barrels (or $1.44 billion) of crude oil over the past five days.\n\n#OOTT #IranWar #Tankers", "time": "08:17", "author": "TankerTrackers", "author_name": "TankerTrackers.com, Inc.", "followers": 227035, "views": 72853, "likes": 467, "replies": 27, "retweets": 127, "quotes": 27, "bookmarks": 57, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067895277818638734", "url": "https://x.com/FluxOfficials/status/2067895277818638734", "text": "KPC announces rescinding Force Majeure and resumption of production thanks to MoU and improving market conditions \n#OOTT #Oil #OilPrices https://t.co/F2303k6RKl", "time": "09:00", "author": "FluxOfficials", "author_name": "The Officials", "followers": 1859, "views": 941, "likes": 6, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2067917185507291486", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067917185507291486", "text": "Iraq to export crude, naphtha through Syria after Hormuz shock #oott https://t.co/nfKcZgwOj3", "time": "10:27", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 13511, "likes": 15, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iraq", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067952745773142491", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067952745773142491", "text": "Here is the administrative requirements to get through the straits of Hormuz \n\nEven when open to all, Iran decides who can pass and when.   \n\nDon’t think of Hormuz as open or closed.    Think of it like a tap that can be open anywhere from a dribble to a jet.   #oott", "time": "12:48", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 1191, "likes": 9, "replies": 4, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2067952923108118844", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067952923108118844", "text": "Iran is requiring all vessels that want to pass the strait to fill in a form on: https://t.co/zHUFxI6rau and gain permission prior to passage #OOTT", "time": "12:49", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 82711, "likes": 163, "replies": 13, "retweets": 39, "quotes": 12, "bookmarks": 20, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2067953678510604302", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067953678510604302", "text": "Senior US Official: Israel, Hezbollah Have Agreed To A Ceasefire At 16:00 Local Time On Friday\n\n#OOTT", "time": "12:52", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 12882, "likes": 34, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2067955710353113545", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067955710353113545", "text": "A senior American official tells me: Israel and Hezbollah have agreed to a renewed ceasefire starting at 16:00 Israel time. The new agreement was reached through US and Qatar mediation after talks with Israel and Iran.\n\n#OOTT", "time": "13:00", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 9775, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2067960874132988409", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067960874132988409", "text": "Sounds like Trump won’t reinstate his blockade on Iranian ships \n\nIf that’s the case it strongly suggests he is fearful of tank bottoms\n\nTank bottoms may be unlikely, but it’s fear of tank bottoms that causes price to spike \n\nHerds don’t react well to fear!  #oott", "time": "13:21", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 4393, "likes": 35, "replies": 3, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2067966334210805872", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067966334210805872", "text": "Think of the odds of Israel leaving Lebanon as equal to the Straits of Hormuz staying open.\n\nThen place time limits on that equation, 1 day, 5 day, 10 day, 30 day, 60 day to establish probabilities.\n\nThen match those with the probabilities of tank bottoms in 30, 60, 90 days #OOTT", "time": "13:42", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 2233, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2067973752101433724", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067973752101433724", "text": "Iran Rejects Claims On Closure Of Strait Of Hormuz – Foreign Ministry\n\n#OOTT", "time": "14:12", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "follo